	   <tr><td colspan=2>Just got one of these on Zebuxoruk for 300pp (which appears to be the fair and going price as of late).<br><br>Great robe with great stats for the price.&nbsp;&nbsp;My next robe upgrade will be to the Froglok Bonecaster's Robe (FBR) which goes for around 3k.<br><br>The INT is very nice for a robe and the 10 svc will come in handy hunting in Velious (or duelling that nasty Shaman).<br><br>My mage is the character that has this and with his own personal buffs and elemental protection items, this 10 svc really adds up.<br><br>I highly recommend this for anyone who can wear it and doesn't have the 3k or more to spend.  You'll get alot of use for it before you find the need to upgrade and spend the plat.<br>&nbsp;<br>======================<br>Madrigan 35 Erudite Magician<br>Itarax 40 Iksar Shaman<br>Vetachi 18 Iksar Monk<br>Balorin 16 Halfling Rogue</td></tr>
