	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ever so often I see the age old and disporved myth that wisdom is necessary for trade skills and helps with success or failure.&nbsp;&nbsp;Unless you are a class that uses wisdom as the base for your mana, wisdom is completely irrelevant for trade skills.  I played an ENC to 53 and was at 214 JC.  My wisdom sucked and I never had any wis gear for JC.  I spoke with several other high level ENCs for JC and all confirmed that wisdom is irrelevant.  Moreover, Abashi, a while back, confirmed that it was irrelevant.  Just to clear things up from personal experience, other's testimony, and Abashi.....wisdom has no effect on trade skills unless you are a say a Druid, where wisdom is the basis for your mana.<br>&nbsp;<br>54th Heretic of Tholuxe Paells (Misty Knight)</td></tr>
